Charles Kane of Spencerport, New York was arrested Thursday as he tried to meet a 14-year-old girl for sex at a movie theater . 
  Kane is a married middle school music teacher with two young daughters . 
  He was arrested when he arrived at the theater with a full box of condoms as the girl was an undercover police officer . 
  Kane had posted a Craigslist ad seeking a young girl for a daddy/daughter relationship . 
  He had been communicating with the girl for months and was arrested after he showed up to meet the girl . 
 